✅ Example Endpoints to Test
Method	Endpoint	Purpose
GET	http://localhost/api/products	Get all products
GET	http://localhost/api/products?category=clothing&minPrice=100&available=true&page=1&pageSize=5	Filtered + paginated products
GET	http://localhost/api/categories	Get all categories
GET	http://localhost/api/categories/clothing/products	Products under a specific category
POST	http://localhost/api/users	Register new user
GET	http://localhost/api/users/u1/orders	Get orders of user u1
POST	http://localhost/api/cart	Add item to cart
GET	http://localhost/api/cart	View user’s cart
